tem_assets/steam/apps/1733860/extras/6f2a3f286fd7c2fed2cb35cae748e9d3.poster.avif?t=1749061887\" width=720 height=312 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1733860/extras/6f2a3f286fd7c2fed2cb35cae748e9d3.webm?t=1749061887\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1733860/extras/6f2a3f286fd7c2fed2cb35cae748e9d3.mp4?t=1749061887\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Open World:</strong> Explore different biomes with unique types of pets and various interesting things!<br></li><li><strong>Build and improve</strong> various devices to improve your factories and create various new resources<br></li><li><strong>Modify and improve</strong> your cannon, as well as various robotic helpers<br></li><li><strong>Find</strong> the most profitable merchants and different characters, hire staff to make it easier to maintain the farm<br></li><li><strong>Defend</strong> your farm and defeat the Lord Dark Head!</li></ul>",
